Interface RandomStream

AlgoRandomStream
All Known Implementing Classes:
AES, ARC4, BBS, BlowFish, CubicResidue, DES, FileAlgoRandomStream, FileRandomStream, HttpGetUrlRandomStream, JavaRandom, JavaSecuredRandom, Lcg1, MicaliSchnorr, ModulusExponent, MT19937, QuadraticResidue1, QuadraticResidue2, RSA, SHA1Random, SkipjackRandom, TokenRandomStream, TripleDES, ZAC3Random, ZAC5Random
public interface RandomStream

RandomStream interface represen stream of data to be checked by the different tests. The interface will be implemented by real classes to read data from files, external devices, web urls or algorithms.

Author:
Zur Aougav
